{"tid":2319450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美媒︰拜登將提名美籍華人戴琦擔任貿易代表","createTime":"2020-12-10T06:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T08:49:36.000Z","uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d23e3ac107a325c2e2ba1d849e435c73925d02e6","tid":2319450,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1564549_1_L_20201210095552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1564549_1_L_20201210095552.jpg&h=b86831ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，總統當選人拜登計劃提名美籍華人、現任眾議院籌款委員會首席貿易律師戴琦（Katherine Tai），擔任美國貿易代表。如果落實，將成為拜登內閣的首位華裔閣員。路透社引述消息人士預計，拜登將在今個星期稍後時間，正式宣布戴琦的提名。<br />\n<br />\n45歲的戴琦畢業於耶魯大學和哈佛大學法學院，能講流利普通話，曾經在廣州中山大學教授英語兩年，擔任過美國貿易代表辦公室總法律顧問，負責處理中國貿易問題。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，戴琦精通中國問題，並具有成熟的外交技巧，提名將表明拜登打算在與盟友密切合作的同時，迅速著手解決懸而未決的貿易問題，以應對中國的經濟競爭。"},{"pid":"4f6c1b9b01608939db8249e6e5237d7c3545bee8","tid":2319450,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:10:14.000Z","msg":"不演了不演了"},{"pid":"6ce14799a333d39451c4b97ba3034e85d3f9d0c7","tid":2319450,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"都就嚟坐監咯仲諗住提名呢個嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9aba497d5eb97ad81edbb1c7bc87ae17ef1881","tid":2319450,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"以夷制夷<br />\n當然最好揾港台，ABC係2nd best"},{"pid":"38130726328ad5b57d840fc6a6748e85ad40b02d","tid":2319450,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"咁出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a418df12dd68f9d5f95a0403f726857e65b297e3","tid":2319450,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d23e3ac107a325c2e2ba1d849e435c73925d02e6","tid":2319450,"uid":172349,"like":0,"d